                "caption": "Figure 3:SE as a projection operator to the clean image manifold.In both panels, the left plot shows LPIPS, and the right shows KID (on a log scale). Step 0 shows the results of the blurred, noisy input before projections.(left)Performance of iteratively applying SE as a projection operator for different values of latent noise. SE projects degraded images to the image manifold, as illustrated by the decrease in the KID score with consecutive steps.(right)Different state-of-the-art VAEs are poor projection operators. SE is illustrated with latent noise of 0.12 on the right.",
